ce:section.ce:para:
The optical properties of the S-CDs@BA composites were investigated. Surprisingly, when the 365 nm UV lamp was turned off, the S-CDs-G@BA, S-CDs-Y@BA and S-CDs-O@BA composites produced green, yellow-green and orange RTP emissions, respectively (Fig. 4
                        ). And the visible phosphorescence duration of S-CDs-G@BA, S-CDs-Y@BA and S-CDs-O@BA composites were about 6, 5, and 4 s, respectively. In order to further investigate this phosphorescence phenomenon, the spectrum data were further measured, as shown in Fig. 5
                        .
